	   <tr><td colspan=2>Clearly, here's a loot item that is designed for all classes.  If you you were loot master on a ToV raid though, you'd prob ask "say aye if you want this".  Some ppl will pass b/c they already have an uber, no drop neck item.  Of the rest you might lean towards a Necro or Shaman ( Int/wis + Mana/Sta/HPs - a rocking combo for these mana coverting classes ) or a hybrid that might benefit from the proc.  Say, a human Pally; an Erudite SK; a human Ranger.  <br><br>In the end, if you had a deserving Barb Warrior, it would be a terrific item for her too.  Some stats will be 'wasted' regardless of who gets it.  Just be happy it dropped :)<br><br>Andred D'Nocte<br>Knight of Paineel<br><br>&nbsp;<br>Andred D'Nocte<br>Knight of Paineel<br>- Fennin Ro - </td></tr>
